#   0 - Success
#   1 - General error
#   2 - Invalid parameters
#   3 - Authentication failed
#   4 - Rate limit exceeded
#   5 - Server error
#   6 - Network error
#   7 - File system error
#   8 - Config error
#   9 - Batch partial failure
#   100 - Unknown error

